=You are helping choose one food-blog recipe idea for LowKeyCooking.

Pick ONE recipe name based on:
- Max prep time: {{ $json.max_prep_time_mins }} minutes
- Skill level: {{ $json.skill_level }}
- Season: {{ $json.season }}
- Ingredient constraints: {{ $json.ingredient_style }}
- Excluded slugs: {{ $json.exclude_recent }}

Requirements:
- Output valid JSON only
- Keep recipe realistic for home cooking
- Prefer recipes with common, easy-to-find ingredients
- Keep ingredient count low: target 6-10 ingredients, never more than 12
- Recipe name must be in English

Return exactly this JSON shape:
{
  "recipe_name": "string",
  "slug": "kebab-case-string",
  "why_fit": "short reason"
}

